{"tid":1428551,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（請推）極陰謀論！炮！灰！狗！隊！","createTime":"2019-08-07T10:10:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T10:34:08.000Z","uid":292067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b2fd03cba08ad79510fb2ed89ca4fbc6013fa8bb","tid":1428551,"uid":292067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:10:07.000Z","msg":"以下為我尻吹<br />\n<br />\n狗隊每日既live係用網絡，再由cctvb經電視播。   每日一方面由網絡挑機，再由電視剪出五同資料比藍絲。  E幾日身邊不停圍繞就係討論狗隊點樣。<br />\n<br />\n某程度狗狗被用黎做炮灰引誘大家。不停高調尻吠令大家去對應，同時不停低調不停控告被捕者。<br />\n<br />\n當全民既怒火同焦點由政府轉移到狗隊身上，建制派就係等一個機會（估9月復會），搶先指責狗隊，然後搶先話要成立調查委員會，將一切既光環攬上身，到時非建制派完全無野可以渣手。再加埋建制派自編自導拉布拖，拖到無左件事（議席上佢地玩哂）。<br />\n<br />\n成件事就變成，政府準備小狗炮灰，比建制收割，係光環加成下，9月復會佢地想點都得。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />pi<br />\n<br />\n預言日期 20190807"},{"pid":"c5e8df8cfd4edbc1cbdcee85673910bb34f23a84","tid":1428551,"uid":292067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:11:31.000Z","msg":"自推十"},{"pid":"c3e9984b2453d684a5457f1db630f97c7825874d","tid":1428551,"uid":292067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:12:07.000Z","msg":"尻"},{"pid":"58292fc357a8f50211255a1206fdc9d31181078f","tid":1428551,"uid":292067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:12:54.000Z","msg":"捌"},{"pid":"06bf9b59081d719c29894dcee844d0a009e250a0","tid":1428551,"uid":292067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:14:15.000Z","msg":"柒"},{"pid":"c250e3b46f86536df984beb6495e538932fe54eb","tid":1428551,"uid":292067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:14:49.000Z","msg":"碌"},{"pid":"293272c4f5c8b5ce04451c6ca477669057b2b689","tid":1428551,"uid":292067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:15:19.000Z"